#: ../../deployment/vllm_omni.rst:3 6a27b58aeb35462ea0b30d953ee67631
msgid "vLLM-Omni"
msgstr "vLLM-Omni"

#: ../../deployment/vllm_omni.rst:5 2b55287088034a53ac762fffdba08d8c
msgid ""
"vLLM-Omni is the official omni-modal serving stack from the vLLM project "
"with native support for VoxCPM2."
msgstr "vLLM-Omni 是 vLLM 项目的官方全模态服务栈，原生支持 VoxCPM2。"

#: ../../deployment/vllm_omni.rst:8 b4cc3b0d4d8a44c491ad691862c8d79f
msgid ""
"Repo: `vllm-project/vllm-omni <https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"omni>`_"
msgstr "仓库：`vllm-project/vllm-omni <https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-omni>`_"

#: ../../deployment/vllm_omni.rst:9 adda7b7d11434ce7ae34661e94be1af4
msgid ""
"VoxCPM2 example: `online_serving/voxcpm2 <https://github.com/vllm-project"
"/vllm-omni/tree/main/examples/online_serving/voxcpm2>`_"
msgstr ""
"VoxCPM2 示例：`online_serving/voxcpm2 <https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"omni/tree/main/examples/online_serving/voxcpm2>`_"

#: ../../deployment/vllm_omni.rst:10 543ba3aabe7649209ab5d54d1871659b
msgid ""
"Installation guide: `vLLM-Omni docs <https://vllm-"
"omni.readthedocs.io/en/latest/getting_started/installation/>`_"
msgstr ""
"安装文档：`vLLM-Omni docs <https://vllm-omni.readthedocs.io/en/latest/getting_started/installation/>`_"

#: ../../deployment/vllm_omni.rst:12 e03cc840c81c474191a550a89b4002c6
msgid ""
"This is the recommended path for production deployments that need "
"concurrent requests, continuous batching, or multi-tenant GPU serving."
msgstr "如果你的生产部署需要并发请求、连续批处理或多租户 GPU 服务，这是当前推荐的方案。"

