#: ../../deployment/vllm_omni.rst:34 2b339042ecab484b9c496b53033d3191
msgid ""
"Install from source. The upstream project is evolving quickly, so prefer "
"the latest main branch unless you have a pinned deployment environment:"
msgstr "建议从源码安装。上游项目迭代较快，除非你的部署环境已经固定版本，否则优先使用最新的 main 分支："

#: ../../deployment/vllm_omni.rst:44 31b2d5f65a8a4c6f9bb37e384a755ed0
msgid ""
"See the upstream installation guide for other platforms such as ROCm, "
"XPU, MUSA, NPU, and Docker-based setups."
msgstr "其他平台（如 ROCm、XPU、MUSA、NPU）以及基于 Docker 的安装方式，请参考上游安装文档。"

