msgstr "部署 VoxCPM2 服务"

#: ../../deployment/vllm_omni.rst:50 19469dfb108b448ba6401be62dc587d1
msgid "Start an OpenAI-compatible TTS server:"
msgstr "启动一个 OpenAI 兼容的 TTS 服务："

#: ../../deployment/vllm_omni.rst:56 13e1c3bb05a54a219d9fdd9946ad4137
msgid "Generate speech from any OpenAI-compatible client:"
msgstr "你可以从任意 OpenAI 兼容客户端发起语音生成请求："

#: ../../deployment/vllm_omni.rst:66 4f37a70b72a34d37a7ae7ae47910fa07
msgid "Notes"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../deployment/vllm_omni.rst:70 799c1cf5bd2d4f1683b0e3f0df2f85ef
msgid ""
"If your workload requires high concurrency, this serving architecture is "
"a better fit than running multiple independent "
"``torch.compile``-optimized VoxCPM processes on the same GPU."
msgstr "如果你的负载需要高并发，这种服务架构通常比在同一张 GPU 上运行多个彼此独立、经过 ``torch.compile`` 优化的 VoxCPM 进程更合适。"

#: ../../deployment/vllm_omni.rst:76 5dc1aec3cc1c4cf89af47a96e3641d92
msgid ""
"For a lighter Python-native serving stack with sync and async APIs, see "
":doc:`NanoVLLM-VoxCPM <nanovllm_voxcpm>`."
msgstr "如果你更需要一个较轻量、原生 Python 的同步 / 异步 API 服务栈，可以参考 :doc:`NanoVLLM-VoxCPM <nanovllm_voxcpm>`。"

